"A Ballad About Green Wood (Czech: Balada o zelen\u00e9m d\u0159evu) is a 1983 Czechoslovak short film written and directed by Ji\u0159\u00ed Barta. It is also known as The Ballad of Green Wood. It tells a story about spring and renewal, portrayed with animated pieces of firewood. It is inspired by the Legend of Vesna from Slavic folklore."